'''吉利熊猫'''在中國以外地區称作 '''Geely LC'''，<ref>[http://www.auto-chinese.com/geely/geely-lc-review-and-road-test-1/ Geely LC (Panda) Review] {{Wayback|url=http://www.auto-chinese.com/geely/geely-lc-review-and-road-test-1/ |date=20120216080029 }} auto-chinese.com 2010-4-12</ref> 是吉利汽车於2009年开始生产的家庭掀背汽车。在2010年[[C-NCAP|C-NCAP]] 撞击测试中，<ref name=fivestar-first/> 吉利熊猫得分达到45.3分，成为中国自主品牌汽车首个<ref name=fivestar-first/> 获得五星级评价的汽车，<ref name=fivestars-chinadaily>[http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/usa/2010-05/04/content_11018409.htm US Geely's growth: Appliances to autos in 13 years] {{Wayback|url=http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/usa/2010-05/04/content_11018409.htm |date=20110923200401 }} chinadaily.com.cn, 2010-05-04</ref> 同时也是中国最安全的掀背汽车<ref name=fivestar-first>{{cite web |url=http://www.geely.com/Brands/international/news/international_news/29855.html |title=Five Star in Collision Test: Geely Panda Appraised as the safest Minicar in China |author= |publisher=[[Geely|Geely International]] |date=2010-01-09 |accessdate=2011-01-22 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101028100700/http://www.geely.com/Brands/international/news/international_news/29855.html |archivedate=2010-10-28 }}</ref>。 

此車車頭燈使用類似貓熊眼睛的設計，車尾燈內則有貓熊的熊掌形狀設計。在2011年，吉利熊猫成为中国[[雅痞|雅皮一族]]热爱的汽车。<ref name=yuppies2/>

==网上销售==
在2010年底<ref name=>[http://autonews.gasgoo.com/china-news/geely-opens-first-online-store-101207.shtml Geely opens first online store] {{Wayback|url=http://autonews.gasgoo.com/china-news/geely-opens-first-online-store-101207.shtml |date=20110711073226 }} gasgoo.com, December 07, 2010</ref>，中国的[[淘宝|淘宝商城]]开始在网上销售吉利熊猫。<ref name=online-chinadaily>[http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/bizchina/2010-12/07/content_11663351.htm China's Geely now selling cars online] {{Wayback|url=http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/bizchina/2010-12/07/content_11663351.htm |date=20201028094315 }} chinadaily.com.cn, 2010-12-07</ref> 尽管买家必须支付288 元保证金，并在购买前需到訪附近的銷售點進行试驾，<ref name=online-reuters/> 而且网上購買的吉利熊猫并不送货到门，<ref>[http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/bizchina/2010-12/08/content_11670643.htm Geely nets online store] {{Wayback|url=http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/bizchina/2010-12/08/content_11670643.htm |date=20200923170217 }} chinadaily.com.cn, 2010-12-08</ref>和購得的型號可能與傳統銷售渠道購得的有分別，<ref name=yuppies2>[http://autos.globaltimes.cn/china/2010-09/572370.html China's Geely eyes online car sales] {{Wayback|url=http://autos.globaltimes.cn/china/2010-09/572370.html |date=20110302232444 }} globaltimes.cn, September 12 2010</ref>网上首日销量依然达到500部。<ref>[http://autonews.gasgoo.com/china-news/geely-s-selling-cars-online-starts-with-a-victory-101224.shtml Geely's selling cars online starts with a victory] {{Wayback|url=http://autonews.gasgoo.com/china-news/geely-s-selling-cars-online-starts-with-a-victory-101224.shtml |date=20101227095846 }} gasgoo.com, December 24, 2010</ref>

